description: Experience luxury living in this stunning 2023 new construction condo in the heart of South Boston! This modern home features 3 large bedrooms with walk in closets and 2 spa-like bathrooms, including a primary suite with a steam shower. The chef’s kitchen is outfitted with premium Thermador appliances, an oversized waterfall kitchen island, detailed lighting, and extends right into your stylish living area with custom built-ins and a cozy gas fireplace. Full size washer/dryer , hardwood throughout, a balcony , an abundance of natural light, TWO PARKING SPACES, and the unbeatable central location puts you within walking distance to South Boston’s top restaurants, bars, and shops. A rare blend of comfort, style, and location make this one you don't want to miss!
